  there  is  a  need  of  charitable  trust  or other similar trusts in our country so that social work should be continued through these  trusts    this  is  a  good  initiative  of  the  government  in  my  opinion    the people of our society should get free medical treatment as such trusts do not spent for the purpose  moreover such trusts do not spent even on education and for the development  of  our  society    amendment  in  article  20  and  20a  alongwith  this amendment  is  a  commendable  effort  of the  government   besides indian  trusts act  also  needs  to  be  amended    it  is  the  responsibility  of  the  corporate  sector  to discharge their csr  but they do not do it  instead they provide their money to the  trusts  and  utilize  the  same  in  other  related  activities    so  the  ministry  of finance  should  fulfill  its  responsibility  by  conducting  regular  monitoring  of  such trusts  i welcome this amendment   